						               													<description>Hydropolis is an abstract city-building game using the components of the game Waterworks.  The &amp;quot;city&amp;quot; starts with one card in the center of the table.  Each turn, you play a card from your hand, score points based on its location relative to other cards, add that play's score to your cumulative score, and then draw a card.  One by one, the table is filled with a contorted maze of pipes.  The game ends when all players pass or when somebody reaches a set amount of points. and the player with the highest running score wins.  But if you earn three Golden Wrenches first, you win automatically!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Complete rules and revision history is available at:&amp;#10;http://ceruleansgames.tripod.com/hydropolis.htm&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
